Title: triptych print
Description: Colour woodblock oban triptych print. Travellers at Enoshima: Collection of elegantly dressed pilgrim travellers waiting at tea-stall at Katase Beach; seven women and one young man taking off hat, fanning breast, wiping perspiration, smoking pipe and re-tying sandal; more tourists watching boys swimming and looking across towards island; snow-capped Mt Fuji in distance. Signed, marked and inscribed.
